{"tid":2408794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致所有有自殺想法嘅人","createTime":"2021-02-15T09:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T10:01:02.000Z","uid":391931,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"remark":"本主題可能正在討論有關「自殺」的內容。\n若你需要進一步協助，可致電以下求助熱線：\n[url]https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline[/url]","replies":[{"pid":"edf4a9a416f65c61257e2e6c8f0c423e429c288e","tid":2408794,"uid":391931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T09:12:51.000Z","msg":"死？唔死？<br />\n<br />\n唔好咁衝動住。<br />\n人總有一死<br />\n但你至少可以選擇<br />\n幾時死 邊到死 點樣死<br />\n<br />\n好好記住<br />\n人係痛哭地降臨世上<br />\n出生 你無法選擇自己出生<br />\n死亡 至少給自己一個自由<br />\n人能帶著笑容離開嗎<br />\n<br />\n食幾餐好嘅  住下大酒店<br />\n享受一下自己未做過嘅嘢<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><br />\n至少不要死在香港！<br />\n至少不要死在香港！<br />\n至少不要死在香港！</span><br />\n<br />\n假如你即將離開這個世界<br />\n不論是什麼傷心絕望原因<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">願你在世最後一刻<br />\n看的是最美的風景<br />\n帶著微笑無悔離開<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：並非教唆他人自殺"},{"pid":"f41529022515f3f9dd41ab9a3bc0c9a11dee0c4c","tid":2408794,"uid":307927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T09:14:12.000Z","msg":"咪死啦 一日唔死呢個世界大把荒謬既野引你笑"},{"pid":"3b55c92ce8e56c0b6c9a627c8ca51c05ca8d97c7","tid":2408794,"uid":304281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T09:15:12.000Z","msg":"咁諗都係好事，去到外國話唔定又唔想死<br />\n有勇氣去死不如把心一橫離開"},{"pid":"645b4de2ab10104aeefd3a0e90e73e9b5af05c32","tid":2408794,"uid":305631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T09:16:02.000Z","msg":"活着需要更大勇氣"},{"pid":"c9d8636c4d00f4e6f524ff0348bcd98a71b6ffed","tid":2408794,"uid":307927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"645b4de2ab10104aeefd3a0e90e73e9b5af05c32","tid":2408794,"uid":305631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T09:16:02.000Z","msg":"活着需要更大勇氣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T09:16:25.000Z","msg":"你或者要 日日開on9 po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bec557f9ca3e64c9b6689b9fdffd22